4.query: Which employees have helped the most customers in Canada?
4.sql:
SELECT e.FirstName, e.LastName, COUNT(c.CustomerId) AS CustomerCount
FROM Employee e
JOIN Customer c ON e.EmployeeId = c.SupportRepId
WHERE c.Country = 'Canada'
GROUP BY e.EmployeeId, e.FirstName, e.LastName
ORDER BY CustomerCount DESC;

5.query: Find the number of tracks in each playlist.
5.sql:
SELECT p.Name, COUNT(pt.TrackId) AS NumberOfTracks
FROM Playlist p
LEFT JOIN PlaylistTrack pt ON p.PlaylistId = pt.PlaylistId
GROUP BY p.Name;

6.query: List the top 5 customers by total purchase amount.
6.sql:
SELECT c.CustomerId, c.FirstName, c.LastName, SUM(i.Total) AS TotalPurchaseAmount
FROM Customer c
JOIN Invoice i ON c.CustomerId = i.CustomerId
GROUP BY c.CustomerId, c.FirstName, c.LastName
ORDER BY TotalPurchaseAmount DESC
LIMIT 5;
